Open widget browser on IOS 7 device -&gt; click to &quot;VirtualSelectBox&quot; form element -&gt; list popup will be appeared over &quot;DateField&quot; -&gt; Try to select &quot;item3&quot; -&gt; result: list disappears but input field focused

Recommended: input field will not be focues</thetext>
